OL,3,CHollywood star among villagers who
OL,4,Chelped reopen much-loved Wiltshire pub
OL,6,FA much-loved Wiltshire pub described
OL,7,Fas the "beating heart" of its village
OL,8,Fhas reopened after being saved by
OL,9,Flocal volunteers.
OL,11,FThe Swan, the only pub in Enford,
OL,12,Fclosed last summer when its previous
OL,13,Fowner left, leaving residents
OL,14,Fdevastated. After several uncertain
OL,15,Fmonths, it is now back open under new
OL,16,Flocal ownership.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
