OL,3,CHollywood star among villagers who
OL,4,Chelped reopen much-loved Wiltshire pub
OL,6,FIt's a "proper community hub" said
OL,7,FSophie Cooper, the new owner. "We have
OL,8,Fall the villagers coming here, some of
OL,9,Fthem wouldn't see anyone else if they
OL,10,Fdidn't come in."
OL,12,FThe reopening has been made possible
OL,13,Fby a team of volunteers who have
OL,14,Fstepped in to serve customers, clean
OL,15,Fand help maintain the pub. Even
OL,16,FHollywood actor Rupert Everett has
OL,17,Fbeen pulling pints behind the bar.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
