OL,3,CHollywood star among villagers who
OL,4,Chelped reopen much-loved Wiltshire pub
OL,6,FThe Swan's revival comes as pubs
OL,7,Facross the region continue to
OL,8,Fstruggle. According to the Campaign
OL,9,Ffor Real Ale (CAMRA), closures have
OL,10,Fdoubled over the past five years, with
OL,11,Fjust under 800 pubs and bars shutting
OL,12,Facross Britain last year alone.
OL,14,FSteve Stringer from CAMRA, said: "It
OL,15,Fgoes back to national insurance rises,
OL,16,Fit goes back to business rates and
OL,17,Fgeneral cost of utilities. It's a hard
OL,18,Ffight for all at the moment."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/4
